task.summary: Attribute definitions should be transformed and added to the Api schema
Implemented AttributeSchemaExtension that appends and extends the schema with types generated from attribute definitions which resolves #3
made several improvements to document processor logic and added a CacheProcessorExtension which resolves #6
Added frontend controller, route and added a basic template for issue #8 Added (untested, wip) links processor for issue #5
implemented very basic webpack build. should be good enough for now.
Changed processor dependency definition properties to before/after and implemented the wildcard as well to resolve #10
Changed keys are now passed on to the mergable childs, resolves #9
Table of content is now generated, but still needs some attention later on. For now it resolves #4
Git addon with both bitbucket and github drivers working
Git addon sync command is working now as well
Git addon webhook controller, needs complete revision
phpdoc attributes with use of annotation in the serializer definitions.
fixed docblock markdown parsing using the parser processor
